01:02.728 --> 01:04.763
known as the "Asch experiment."

01:04.796 --> 01:07.099
This experiment tests conformity

01:07.132 --> 01:08.233
and whether or not a person

01:08.266 --> 01:10.203
will say something incorrect

01:10.236 --> 01:12.271
simply because everyone else is.

01:12.304 --> 01:13.539
What matters more?

01:13.572 --> 01:15.575
Being right or fitting in?

01:15.608 --> 01:18.578
<i> [calm music]</i>

01:18.611 --> 01:20.213
