01:31.290 --> 01:33.392
a real participant who has no idea

01:33.424 --> 01:36.361
<i>what's going on will be seated.</i>

01:36.394 --> 01:39.598
Now, their task is to
match the length of the line

01:39.632 --> 01:42.802
