01:48.908 --> 01:50.242
and say what you saw,

01:50.275 --> 01:52.144
or would you just fit in

01:52.177 --> 01:55.280
because it's easier
or less uncomfortable?

01:55.313 --> 01:56.448
Well, let's find out.

01:59.385 --> 02:01.287
So welcome, everyone. My name's Ron.

02:01.319 --> 02:03.822
