02:15.266 --> 02:16.536
<i>say the correct answer</i>

02:16.568 --> 02:17.836
<i>to gain the trust of our subject.</i>

02:17.870 --> 02:20.772
<i>The correct answer here is three.</i>

02:20.806 --> 02:21.774
Three.

