06:53.879 --> 06:55.713
<i>Even laughter is a form of conformity.</i>

06:55.747 --> 06:57.583
<i>We laugh if something is funny,</i>

06:57.615 --> 06:58.950
<i>but we also tend to laugh</i>

06:58.983 --> 07:00.919
<i>if people around us are laughing,</i>

07:00.952 --> 07:02.754
<i>even if we don't get the joke.</i>

07:02.788 --> 07:05.790
<i>There are a lot of
social forces behind this:</i>

07:05.824 --> 07:09.061
politeness, a fear of looking stupid,

07:09.093 --> 07:12.031
and no doubt a desire to conform...

07:12.064 --> 07:13.933
to fit in.

07:13.966 --> 07:16.836
Let's see what happens when
there's even more pressure

07:16.869 --> 07:19.038
